GnomeSwitchTimerMin.Description: A new random value is picked after each time a Respawnable moves. The random value must be taken within a MIN (this variable) and MAX boundary values that must be settable by the design.

GnomeSwitchTimerMax.Description: A new random value is picked after each time a Respawnable moves. The random value must be taken within a MIN and MAX (this variable) boundary values that must be settable by the design.
